These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, begonia, lily, iris
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, family, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, metal, salsa, electronic
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, motorbike, taxi
 1. the fan of metal is not to the right of the fan of ambient##8
 2. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the fan of ambient is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
 5. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
 6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 7. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the right of the person who growsrose##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is between the person driving the jet-ski and the fan of metal##2
 9. the person driving the taxi is the person watching family movies##1
10. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
11. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
12. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbegonia##5
13. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
14. the person who growsbegonia is the person driving the motorbike##1
15. the person who growsbegonia is not the fan of metal##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Flower         | rose     | begonia   | iris | lily |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery   | animation   | family  |
| Music-Genre         | metal  | salsa  | electronic  | ambient |
| Transport     | airplane    | motorbike | jet-ski     | taxi    |

