.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
City: new-york, nizza, hamburg, london
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, begonia, tulip, rose
 1. the fan of salsa is between the person who growslily and the fan of indie##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person who growsbegonia##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person who growsrose##8
 5. the person who growslily is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person traveling to london is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the left of the person who growsrose##5
 8. the person who growstulip is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the person who growsbegonia##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
11. the person who growslily is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to nizza##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the person traveling to nizza is not to the right of the person who growsbegonia##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| City          | london     | nizza | new-york | hamburg  |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | salsa  | trance | house |
| Flower           | tulip | rose | lily    | begonia  |

