4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, ritmeester, game, chaman
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, august, january, february
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person watching mystery movies##8
 7. the game-smoker is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
10. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
11. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##8
12. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | sudoku   | skydiving | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | mystery  | western   | drama      |
