.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, tea, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, jazz, rock, folk
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, nigerian, thai
There 4 different types of food: lime, zucchini, broccoli, apricot
 1. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 2. the person eating lime is not to the left of the fan of folk##8
 3. the person eating lime is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 5. the person eating broccoli is the nigerian##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the dutch##8
 7. the person drinking sprite is not the thai##6
 8. the fan of jazz is somewhere between the person eating broccoli and the person drinking sprite##7
 9. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
10. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
11. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
12. the fan of jazz is not the argentine##6
13. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
15. the person eating lime is not to the right of the fan of jazz##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | sprite    | water   | tea        | iced-tea  |
| Music-Genre           | folk     | jazz | r&b | rock  |
| Nationality   | argentine | thai    | nigerian   | dutch     |
| Food     | apricot       | lime     | broccoli    | zucchini |

