.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
House: modern, townhouse, cottage, futuristic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
4 different pets are kept: hamster, bird, mouse, pony
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, snowmobile
 1. the cottage house is the owner of the pony##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the modern house is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
 8. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
10. the townhouse house is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the futuristic house##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| House      | modern   | futuristic     | cottage    | townhouse |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul      | reggae     | folk     |
| Pet         | hamster | mouse  | pony     | bird  |
| Transport     | bike     | quad-bike | snowmobile | boat     |

