There 4 different types of food: pineapple, asparagus, lemon, avocado
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##8
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
 4. the person traveling to berlin is the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person traveling to prague##6
 6. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the person eating asparagus##8
 7. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the person traveling to prague##8
 8. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 9. the person eating lemon is in an even position##4
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person traveling to prague and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
